<p>Small and Medium size Enterprises are getting increasingly involved in
community projects. GNU/Linux distributions have a great opportunity of
creating a symbiotic relation with them, now that Free Software is getting
mainstream.</p>

<p>Can be the future of distributions linked somehow to SME? How? What are those
advantages distributions can offer to SME? How can we make these community
projects more attractive to SME?</p>

<p>I will give answer the above questions and other similar from my own
experience and point of view.</p>
